{"tid":969322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨郭紹傑和嚴敏華家人赴日 入境處派員公幹","createTime":"2019-01-05T03:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:10:32.000Z","uid":53524,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16f1b2c95cea785a827813dfba67eda954f801ee","tid":969322,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"保釣行動委員會表示，上月到日本靖國神社外抗議而被捕的郭紹傑和嚴敏華，他們的家人包括郭紹傑女兒及嚴敏華母親，將於今晚乘坐飛機前往日本，探望兩人。<br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會說，入境處會派員同行，而家屬到日本後將會見日本律師和向駐日中國大使館尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n駐日中國大使館未有回應事件。"},{"pid":"ee6560c8cc71e9cad00354f72f2360956e0300a7","tid":969322,"uid":10905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"做入境處真係好<br />\n輪流去旅行"},{"pid":"055282d4255110ea29818100156576c9dbd9bfcd","tid":969322,"uid":45857,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"屋企人又幾爽，無啦啦有得去日本玩，探人頂多探一日，至於其餘既時間.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf5782b4e69e37ea12612fea137dd5928235240","tid":969322,"uid":40839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee6560c8cc71e9cad00354f72f2360956e0300a7","tid":969322,"uid":10905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"做入境處真係好<br />\n輪流去旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"出trip未必好<br />\n啲家屬一定煩到你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17eca4503dc0493ec866a5872bfe857d9ce20a9a","tid":969322,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"6d9390b88449fa7b387fc6d00df5504c4db3ad8e","tid":969322,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"c26dcd95a571ba427a49e8b60c809cd0bf38b89d","tid":969322,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc